---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Get Involved | IdiomasPuentes">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Get Involved</h1>
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center mb-12">
      <div class="md:w-1/2 mb-8 md:mb-0">
        <img src="/images/get-involved.jpg" alt="Get Involved" class="rounded-lg shadow-lg" />
      </div>
      <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-8">
        <p class="text-xl mb-8">There are many ways to support the mission of IdiomasPuentes and contribute to the work of Bible translation:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-lg mb-8">
          <li>Pray for the work of Bible translation and the tribal churches</li>
          <li>Volunteer your skills in translation, technology, or administration</li>
          <li>Partner with us financially to support ongoing projects</li>
          <li>Spread awareness about the importance of Bible translation</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-xl mb-8">By getting involved, you're helping to bring God's Word to communities in their heart language, fostering spiritual growth and transformation.</p>
        <a href="mailto:info@idiomaspuentes.org" class="bg-blue-500 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-blue-600 transition duration-300">Contact Us to Get Involved</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
